给予每位入选选手纪念与荣耀他们生涯的通行证，但我们创造来纪念他们成就的风格装饰种类，可能会随着我们更加了解玩家需求而改变。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ad168a3735ee744ffb58b39ef83dd891_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657661201"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I66eM29bJ29wWEAMaCTEwODQyNDc2MyCu+eCyBjAAOElAJXIJNjU3NjYxMjAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1717208961.958127", "card_id": "Q_653198967", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何利用心理学原理提高学习效率和工作效率？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c8b24b5d270a88d292b96bb1c0e9ad85_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653198967"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI66eM29bJ29wWEAMaCTEwNzQzMjk5MiDwnPywBjAAOP0BQCZyCTY1MzE5ODk2N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1717208961.958426", "card_id": "Q_657078050", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 82}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在职场上你认为最宝贵的经验是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-15c9885c2487fb2333d49b0005fa6ae6_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "26 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657078050"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI66eM29bJ29wWEAMaCTEwODI5NTI1MCC3lcSyBjAAOMcBQCdyCTY1NzA3ODA1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1717208961.958760", "card_id": "Q_657329993", "feed_specific